    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out per the approved MRL 2 assessment plan with documented justification. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions as a Class II device. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
